* 0.4.0 (2020-01-07)

  * accept stdin as input
  * output to dir/bundle.css if output is a directory

* 0.3.2 (2018-09-21)

  * automatically add .css extension to input, if not provided
  * check if output file or directory exists
  * automatically add filename if output is a directory
  * check for input and output permissions

* 0.3.1 (2018-09-12)

  * add changelog
  * updated dependencies: chalk, chokidar, meow
